Developer Tea is a podcast hosted by Jonathan Cutrell that focuses on soft skills for software developers.
In the April 3rd 2017 episode Jonathan answers a listener question and elaborates on strategies to build &ldquo;reliable behavioural systems&rdquo;
I first got in touch with the concept of &ldquo;systems vs goals&rdquo; in [Scott Adam]&rsquo;s book How to Fail at Almost Everything and Still Win Big: Kind of the Story of My Life Kindle Edition.
